name: Tsel%27rbah
content:
Tsel'rbah was a female Twi'lek major of the Galactic Republic, stationed at the Carrick Station during the Cold War and Galactic War.
Major Tsel'rbah appeared in the video game Star Wars: The Old Republic, where she gave Republic players on Carrick Station the bonus series for Nar Shaddaa. She, along with her Imperial counterpart Agent Velloo and the Alderaan bonus series mission givers, were removed in Game Update 4.1.
